 DATE/       Date of flight (in case of PPL)
 EET/        Significant points or FIR codes with time of their reaching

 STS/        significant status of flight, i.e. for life rescue (STS/HOSP)

 RIF/        Destination aerodrome changed
 DEP/        Departure aerodrome if in array 13 is 'ZZZZ' or 'AFIL'
 DEST/       Destination aerodrome if in array 16 is 'ZZZZ' or 'AFIL'
 ALTN/       Suplementary aerodrome if in array 16 is 'ZZZZ'
 RALT/       Suplementary aerodrome for route

 REG/        Aircraft reistration different from 7a
 SEL/        SELCAL code
 OPR/        Flight operator

 TYP/        Type of aircraft, if in array 9 is 'ZZZZ'

 COM/
 NAV/
 DAT/        Data link
 PER/        Aircraft performance

 RMK/
